org.mybatis.dynamic.sql

Interface BindableColumn<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - - even though the type is not directly used in this class, it is used by the compiler to match columns with conditions so it should not be removed.
    All Superinterfaces:
    BasicColumn
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Add, BaseFunction, Lower, SqlColumn, Substring, Upper

    public interface BindableColumn<T>
extends BasicColumn
    Describes additional attributes of columns that are necessary for binding the column as a JDBC parameter. Columns in where clauses are typically bound.
    Author:
    Jeff Butler
